  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "Complete\nfolder 49 - 013\nare undermined. reality is thwarted - changed in a way that aborts its ability to process the info on which it is dependent in order to function. Not only is _your_ script amended (or nullified) but _its_ script is amended (or nullified). Hence we speak of Christ as Pantocrator : Lord of the Universe.\n\nNow, look how this fits in with Buddhism. The world is viewed as cruel & murderous & karmic. Both Christ & the Buddha propose ways to escape from this cruel, occluding tyr",
      "matched_alias": "Buddhism",
      "term_id": "TERM_buddhism",
      "term_name": "Buddhism",
      "term_slug": "buddhism"
    },
    {
      "text": "Now, if my 2-(3-74) is the paradigmatic actual 8-stage extrication -- well, how common is it? Presumably everyone else is still in the grip of the elemental powers just as I was before 2-74. But the experience is available otherwise it couldn't have happened to me. It has more of the aspect of the waking up that constitutes becoming a Buddha -- a rare event, & all Buddhas are manifestations of the one external Buddha -- which fits my impression of 3-74. However, it was not --\n\nI remembered; that",
      "matched_alias": "Buddhism",
      "term_id": "TERM_buddhism",
      "term_name": "Buddhism",
      "term_slug": "buddhism"
    },
    {
      "text": "are undermined. reality is thwarted - changed in a way that aborts its ability to process the info on which it is dependent in order to function. Not only is _your_ script amended (or nullified) but _its_ script is amended (or nullified). Hence we speak of Christ as Pantocrator : Lord of the Universe.\n\nNow, look how this fits in with Buddhism. The world is viewed as cruel & murderous & karmic. Both Christ & the Buddha propose ways to escape from this cruel, occluding tyranny which creates so muc",
      "matched_alias": "Judaism",
      "term_id": "TERM_judaism",
      "term_name": "Judaism",
      "term_slug": "judaism"
    },
    {
      "text": "(1) the 8-step Xtian salvific experience occurred to me (so it does exist)\n\n(2) but scarcely anyone else reports it : it is the waking up of the Buddha, not a mass experience & (alas) not really occurring due simply to \"accepting Christ.\" Rather, it is a culmination of a number of lifetimes - in my case stretching back over 3000 years to Egyptian Crete. &, before that, to the Stars.\n\nIt is connected to Orphism, the Elysian Mysteries & the Greco-Roman Mystery religions. It is an attempt to rememb",
      "matched_alias": "Orphism",
      "term_id": "TERM_orphism",
      "term_name": "Orphism",
      "term_slug": "orphism"
    }
  ],
